commit_message:
RN6.0-updates2 Glance resolved issues

This patch adds Glance resolved issues:

* Glance user storage quota bypass;
* connection reset by peer during glance
  image-create with vcenter back end;
* can't upload image by link from slow source;
* /tmp is not cleaned after image upload from horizon.

Change-Id: Ibe55b6058fbcea30c812c0f6d2957543277a89ae
